{"tid":2492510,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"歐盟警告港府檢控民主派將影響歐中關係    英國外相呼籲港府停止檢控民主派　","createTime":"2021-04-17T07:11:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-17T07:37:55.000Z","uid":204533,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8084c7ca4924c5a935ab52382604b6c96ff829fd","tid":2492510,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T07:11:27.000Z","msg":"英國外相拉布（Dominic Raab）說，和平示威是香港的基本生活方式，受到中英聯合聲明和基本法保障，應該予以肯定。他聲言英國會繼續與港人站在一起。不過，黎智英擁有英國國籍，但英國外交部之前曾表示不能向他提供領事協助，因為中國不承認雙重國籍。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，歐盟外交和安全政策高級代表波瑞爾（Josep Borrell）的發言人透過聲明警告，香港多名民主派元老因非法集結被判刑，損害香港的基本自由和「影響歐盟與中國關係」。<br />\n<br />\n發言人說：「一些人士因行使受保障的公民權進行非暴力活動，而遭長期監禁，進一步顯示民主空間繼續收窄，侵蝕香港的基本自由。這些在香港發生的事情，令人質疑中國履行國際承諾的意願，損害歐盟與中國之間的信任和關係。」"},{"pid":"0bcd0e4b0253168c0e92dbe6d11830c9af944ec7","tid":2492510,"uid":204533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T07:11:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210417/GFATEIDRLBBI5BK7XHDKVEI3KY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210417%2FGFATEIDRLBBI5BK7XHDKVEI3KY%2F&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CL%2FFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=9f84a1c7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210417%2FGFATEIDRLBBI5BK7XHDKVEI3KY%2F&h=51192159\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210417/GFATEIDRLBBI5BK7XHDKVEI3KY/</a>"},{"pid":"1bdda39d8ecfc3e820051767198c24e38b7254eb","tid":2492510,"uid":115579,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T07:12:05.000Z","msg":"國安法拉左人地外相未"},{"pid":"628637281fbede8e336783f33f7d6313ebcb9674","tid":2492510,"uid":316667,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T07:12:41.000Z","msg":"真係好嬲好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n收皮啦英狗得把口"},{"pid":"1650a8a47b95204ee41f993488b213a1247d8773","tid":2492510,"ui